 )}} |-| ''Setter''|| set_tilt(value)     |-| ''Getter''|| get_tilt()          |}Represents the angles of tilt of the pen. Positive X-coordinate value indicates a tilt to the right. Positive Y-coordinate value indicates a tilt toward the user. Ranges from {{Span|-1.0}} to {{Span|1.0}} for both axes.